Package org.joda.beans.impl

Class BasicImmutableBeanBuilder<T extends Bean>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joda.beans.impl.BasicImmutableBeanBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the bean type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanBuilder<T>
    public abstract class BasicImmutableBeanBuilder<T extends Bean>
extends Object
implements BeanBuilder<T>
    Basic implementation of BeanBuilder that wraps a MetaBean.

    The subclass implementation generally has concrete fields for each property. This class has effectively been replaced by DirectFieldsBeanBuilder. It is retained for situations where the builder is being implemented manually.
